      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行需要时间来权衡通胀不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，目前还没有足够的证据表明通胀威胁已经过去——这加剧了人们对央行本月将暂停降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
